SUMMARY:State of AI : Context Engineering with Microsoft and Anthropic
DESCRIPTION:Modern Web (Triangle)\nContext is becoming a defining layer of
  modern AI systems and is shaping how models reason\, respond\, and integr
 ate into real products. This event explores how context engineering is inf
 luencing the current state of AI and the way teams are thinking about buil
 ding more capable and reliable systems.\n\n[Join us for a conversation](ht
 tps://luma.com/79w48jgi) with experts from Microsoft and Anthropic as we e
 xamine emerging approaches to structuring context\, lessons from real-worl
 d AI development\, and the considerations guiding what comes next.\n\nFeat
 uring insights from\n[Harald Kirschner](https://www.linkedin.com/in/digita
 rald/)\, Principal Product Manager for GitHub Copilot and VS Code at Micro
 soft\n[Ado Kukic](https://www.linkedin.com/in/adocomplete/)\, Community Ma
 nager at Anthropic\n[Brandon Mathis](https://www.linkedin.com/in/mathisbra
 ndon/)\, Engineering Lead\, This Dot Labs\n[Tracy Lee](https://www.linkedi
 n.com/in/tracyslee/)\, CEO\, This Dot Labs\n\n[If you are interested in at
 tending\, please RSVP using this link!](https://luma.com/iho7wvqp)
