SUMMARY:State of React Native
DESCRIPTION:Modern Web (Triangle)\nExplore how React Native continues to e
 volve as a leading framework for building high-quality cross-platform appl
 ications.\n\n​We’re bringing together mobile engineers\, technical lea
 ders\, product teams\, and community contributors to share real-world use 
 cases\, best practices\, and the latest advancements in the React Native e
 cosystem. Join us to discuss what’s new\, what’s next\, and how teams 
 are building faster\, more scalable mobile experiences.\n\nFeaturing\n[Gan
 t Laborde](https://www.linkedin.com/in/gant-laborde/)\, CIO and Founder\, 
 Infinite Red\n[Mazen Chami](https://www.linkedin.com/in/mazenchami/)\, Sta
 ff Software Engineer\, Infinite Red\n[Tracy Lee](https://www.linkedin.com/
 in/tracyslee/)\, CEO\, This Dot Labs\n\n[Learn more and RSVP.](https://lum
 a.com/m5etppc8)
